Interface OobResponse

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IdpResult
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    OobFetchMessageResponse, OobMessageResponse, OobNotificationProfilesResponse, OobRegistrationResponse

    public interface OobResponse
extends IdpResult
    Extends the IdpResult in order to define the user data keys specific for the OOB subsystem.
